<doc id="452238" wikidata="Q253074" url="?curid=452238" title="List of cities in North Dakota">
<text>North Dakota is a state located in the Midwestern United States. All incorporated communities in North Dakota are considered cities, regardless of population; there are no towns, villages, or hamlets in the state. There are 355 municipalities.

==Cities==


